### FinanceAI API — sample requests (VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP)
### Set @token and @org after signup/login + create org.

@base = http://localhost:4000/api/v1
@token = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN
@org = PASTE_ORG_ID

### Health
GET http://localhost:4000/health

### Signup
POST {{base}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "founder@acme.test", "password": "supersecret123", "fullName": "Ada Founder" }

### Login
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "founder@acme.test", "password": "supersecret123" }

### Create organization (tenant)
POST {{base}}/organizations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Acme Studio", "currency": "USD" }

### Dashboard KPIs
GET {{base}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Org-Id: {{org}}

### Create expense (auto-categorized by Gemma/heuristic)
POST {{base}}/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Org-Id: {{org}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "amount": 52.99, "rawDescription": "ADOBE *CREATIVE CLOUD" }

### List expenses (filter + paginate)
GET {{base}}/expenses?status=pending&limit=25&page=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Org-Id: {{org}}

### Create invoice
POST {{base}}/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Org-Id: {{org}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "clientName": "Globex Inc", "lineItems": [{ "description": "Redesign", "quantity": 1, "unitPrice": 3500 }], "taxRate": 8.5, "dueDate": "2026-08-01" }

### Download invoice PDF
GET {{base}}/invoices/INVOICE_ID/pdf
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Org-Id: {{org}}

### AI CFO chat
POST {{base}}/ai/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Org-Id: {{org}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "question": "How healthy is my cash position this year?" }

### Natural-language search
POST {{base}}/ai/search
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Org-Id: {{org}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "query": "show software expenses over 50 this year" }

### Profit & Loss
GET {{base}}/reports/pl
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Org-Id: {{org}}

### Billing plans (public)
GET {{base}}/billing/plans
